  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p971526/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/16/d108e456cfec69956958db13f64b3845.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThe 1970s must have taken place on a different planet. These photos of men&rsquo;s fashions from that decade leave us drowning in astounding mustard knits, garish patterns, high waists, way-too-skimpy briefs, and other fashion faux pas that defy description 40 years later.20世纪70年代仿佛就是来自另一个星球的时代。这些来自70年代的男性时尚的照片充斥着令人震惊的芥末色针织衫、花哨俗丽的图案、高腰裤、又短又紧的三角裤，还有其他如今已经变得不可描述的时尚。</p>\n<p>\n\tAs synthetics fell in price, casual menswear was suddenly available to many young men looking to cut loose. Since polyester doesn&rsquo;t require ironing, the &ldquo;wash and wear&rdquo; revolution is in full view of these models with their skin-tight threads.随着人工合成面料的降价，休闲男装突然就成为了广大年轻男士追求时尚的选择。由于聚酯面料无需熨烫，&ldquo;免烫快干&rdquo;革命便开始随着模特们的紧身裤兴起了。</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/16/2c990ff53326ea94272dffb4aa33ceeb.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/16/8e642d0cacd11322a995cce5ffd1cda7.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/16/f4f177795b45dc5164f2112297702d8b.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/16/4a210f18e70b6789ae22a2dbf0982b29.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/16/a4db4413dfad388784417bb8f718f660.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/16/0c55e0cc13c6c74ce83963b555f694fc.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/16/b4dbec2014f8de2188f06ba1cf3df56c.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://n1image.hjfile.cn/mh/2016/12/16/c129e2d181121c4b5851aad4012af7cc.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #999999;\">\n\t声明：本双语文章的中文翻译系沪江英语原创内容，转载请注明出处。中文翻译仅代表译者个人观点，仅供参考。如有不妥之处，欢迎指正。</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglis